      "date": "2014-08-14 15:04:45.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1: Code-Review-1\n\nLooks ok, but it break the compilation on ubuntu. There is 2 definition for cfs_size_round() and following the re-ordering in lustre_cfg.h, the wrong one is picked up. Changing the version in lustre_user.h fixes the error.\n\n-static inline int cfs_size_round (int val)\n+static inline size_t cfs_size_round(size_t val)\n\nHowever the real fix is to have just one version of cfs_size_round().",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 1
    },
